#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_armor_stand/init.lua:53
msgid "Armor Stand"
msgstr "Armadurarako euskarria"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_armor_stand/init.lua:54
msgid "Displays pieces of armor"
msgstr "Armadura-piezak erakusten ditu"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_armor_stand/init.lua:55
msgid ""
"An armor stand is a decorative object which can display different pieces of "
"armor. Anything which players can wear as armor can also be put on an armor "
"stand."
msgstr ""
"Armadurarako euskarria objektu apaingarri bat da, armadura-pieza desberdinak "
"erakuts ditzakeena. Jokalariek armadura gisa erabil dezaketen edozer gauza "
"armadurarako euskarri batean ere jar daiteke."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_armor_stand/init.lua:56
msgid ""
"Just place an armor item on the armor stand. To take the top piece of armor "
"from the armor stand, select your hand and use the place key on the armor "
"stand."
msgstr ""
"Armadura-item bat jartzen du armadurarako euskarrian. Armadurarako "
"euskarriaren goiko armadura-pieza hartzeko, hautatu zure eskua eta erabili "
"posizio-tekla armadurarako euskarrian."
